tegory issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.18 (June 29, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Chat table regeneration issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.17 (June 07, 2022)<br \\/>\\n<strong>Added<\\/strong>: App Woo payment support<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.16 (May 18, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Stripe text translation issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Custom Field select\\/checkbox filter issue<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Layout style<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.15 (May 10, 2022)<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Guzzle PHP client https:\\/\\/docs.guzzlephp.org<br \\/>\\nFixed: translation issue for stripe payment getaway<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.12 (April 11, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Elementor Archive &amp; Single Page Builder Addon compatibility<br \\/>\\nAdded: Per sign control in the Pricing Box addon<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.10 (March 01, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Backend widget area console error<br \\/>\\nAdded: Pricing Table Gutenberg block<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.9 (Feb 16, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Gutenberg Blacks (Listings, Listings category, All locations, Singe location,<br \\/>\\ncategory slider, listing slider)<br \\/>\\nVersion 2.0.8 (Jan 20, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Compatible with free version 2.1.0<br \\/>\\nAdded: Elementor Widget<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.7 (Jan 04, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Push notification translation.<br \\/>\\nFixed: Radius search filter widget translation.<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.5.2 (Dec 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Stripe IOS payment issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: comment form script<br \\/>\\nAdd: Rating filter<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.5.2 (Dec 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Free &amp; Pro version dependency <\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.5.1 (Dec 13, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Fix option error.<br \\/>\\nFixed: Remove unwanted localization for map.<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.5 (Dec 09, 2021)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Re-captcha V 3<br \\/>\\nAdd: OpenStreetMap<br \\/>\\nUpdate: API update for Map<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.3 (Nov 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Add google social login using google firebase<br \\/>\\nVersion 2.0.2.6 (Nov 04, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Push notification table column rename issue<br \\/>\\nVersion 2.0.2.5 (Oct 27, 2021)<br \\/>\\nAdd push notifications for app<br \\/>\\nVersion 2.0.2.4 (Sep 28, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Review template<br \\/>\\nAdd: Stripe 3D SAP secure payment Option<br \\/>\\nUpdate: coding structure<br \\/>\\nAdd: orders and orders\\/xxxxxx rest API<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.2.3 (Sep 14, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFix: conditional field issue for multilingual<br \\/>\\nFix: multilingual custom field delete issue<br \\/>\\nUpdate: payment rtcl-api end point<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Rest api end point<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.2.2 (Aug 13, 2021)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Seller Contact information for register user.<br \\/>\\nFix: Map marker issue<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Rest API <\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.2.1 (July 28, 2021)<br \\/>\\nBugfix: Custom fields filtering.<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.2 (July 16, 2021)<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Rest API<br \\/>\\nBugfix: Some bug fix.<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.1 (Jun 28, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFix: REST API issue fixed<br \\/>\\nFix: Classified listing free version dependency Update<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.0 (Jun 24, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFix: Map control.<br \\/>\\nFix: Password Reset link.<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Update code to work on free version. Now need to install free version first.<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.73.9 (May 07, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Membership issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Ordering issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Compare issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Pending post expired text issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Apply filter button hide issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Listing image resize error issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.73.7 (April 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: App data connect issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.73.5 (Feb 14, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Membership issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Unregistered user posting ad issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: Pricing range and disable feature<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.73.2 (Feb 11, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Forgot password issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Listing post edit alert issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Compare responsive issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Vers