re set feature image when upload logo<br \\/>\\nAdded: Add description to membership oder details and order receipt page<br \\/>\\nUpdated:  Hide free ads if free ads off and membership is on<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.8 (Mar 15, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Edit membership edit issue<br \\/>\\nUpdate: membership menu UI<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.7 (Feb 22, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Pay per ad membership promotion issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.6 (Feb 20, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store category display issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Logo\\/banner update issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: Option for store review process<br \\/>\\nAdded: Badge for membership users<br \\/>\\nAdded: Badge for store owner<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store only for verified user [Seller Verification addon]<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.5 (Feb 05, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Form Builder Compatibility<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store RTL issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.3 (Nov 20, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: My-account style issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.1 (Nov 08, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: User Dashboard backward compatibility<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.5.0 (Nov 07, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: New dashboard compatibility<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.33 (Sep 25, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Website link display issue<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Social Profile list<br \\/>\\nAdded:  Store rest api config<br \\/>\\nAdded: Category filter<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.32 (July 25, 2023)<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Membership api for APP<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.31 (July 25, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Add hook to remove nonce from contact form<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.30 (June 23, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Hook for carry forward expired membership data<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.29 (April 28, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: PHP 8.2 compatibility<br \\/>\\nAdded: Login redirect to a single page for store contact<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.28 (Mar 09, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Pagination for Elementor Store addon<br \\/>\\nAdded: Settings for store pagination and grid column<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.27 (Mar 01, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Renew issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: