c 22, 2025)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Accessibility issues<br \\/>\\nFixed: Twitter\\/X icon issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 3.0.3 (Oct 15, 2025)<br \\/>\\nUpdate : New settings layout compatibility<br \\/>\\nVersion 3.0.2 (Aug 15, 2025)<br \\/>\\nUpdate : Rest API for store banner and owner<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 3.0.1 (July 28, 2025)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Pay per ads settings<br \\/>\\nVersion 3.0.0 (July 01, 2025)<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Reorganized admin settings<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.1.1 (June 13, 2025)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Author listing query issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.1.0 (May 27, 2025)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Toolkit addon compatibility<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.3 (May 14, 2025)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Membership pricing selection issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store open\\/close time zone issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.1 (May 07, 2025)<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Page layout<br \\/>\\nFixed: AJAX filter issue in store details page<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store logo set issue as featured<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.1 (Mar 21, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Twitter icon issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store information at listing REST API<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Social profile options from main plugin<br \\/>\\nOptimisation: Store logo and banner image size generation<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 2.0.0 (Dec 20, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Text domain issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store category menu active issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Notice issue<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Post log count<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store whatsapp number<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.11 (Nov 15, 2024)<br \\/>\\nAdded: WhatsApp number for store<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.5.10 (Oct 01, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: business hour translation issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Migrated old business structure<br \\/>\\nFixed: store opening ours from admin end<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.9 (April 23, 2024)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store set feature image when upload logo<br \\/>\\nAdded: Add description to membership oder details and order receipt page<br \\/>\\nUpdated:  Hide free ads if free ads off and membership is on<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.8 (Mar 15, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Edit membership edit issue<br \\/>\\nUpdate: membership menu UI<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.7 (Feb 22, 2024)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Pay per ad membership promotion issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.6 (Feb 20, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store category display issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Logo\\/banner update issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: Option for store review process<br \\/>\\nAdded: Badge for membership users<br \\/>\\nAdded: Badge for store owner<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store only for verified user [Seller Verification addon]<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.5 (Feb 05, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Form Builder Compatibility<br \\/>\\nFixed: Store RTL issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.3 (Nov 20, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: My-account style issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.5.1 (Nov 08, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: User Dashboard backward compatibility<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.5.0 (Nov 07, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: New dashboard compatibility<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.33 (Sep 25, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Website link display issue<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Social Profile list<br \\/>\\nAdded:  Store rest api config<br \\/>\\nAdded: Category filter<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.32 (July 25, 2023)<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Membership api for APP<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.31 (July 25, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Add hook to remove nonce from contact form<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.30 (June 23, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Hook for carry forward expired membership data<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.29 (April 28, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: PHP 8.2 compatibility<br \\/>\\nAdded: Login redirect to a single page for store contact<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.28 (Mar 09, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Pagination for Elementor Store addon<br \\/>\\nAdded: Settings for store pagination and grid column<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.27 (Mar 01, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Renew issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: Shortcode class load issue <\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.26 (Feb 15, 2023)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Free ads count in dashboard statistics<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.25 (Jan 11, 2023)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Free and membership post count issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: New new new option for all users \\/ Only membership<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.24 (Dec 06, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Listing renew from membership<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.4.23 (Nov 25, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Javascript issue with checkout<br \\/>\\nAdded: Added some hooks for the free version<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.21 (Sep 14, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store review compatibility with Review Schema<br \\/>\\nFixed: Session error log<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.20 (Aug 12, 2022)<br \\/>\\nUpdated: Security &amp; Sanitisation<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Change text naming<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.19 (July 25, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Day start issue<br \\/>\\nAdded: Coupon addon compatibility<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.18 (July 06, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Week starts on from settings<br \\/>\\nFixed: Membership regular ad field issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.17 (Jul 01, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: New Feature for Store Single Page builder.<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.4.14 (May 10, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: PHP Warning issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.12 (April 12, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store Grid\\/List Elementor Addon<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.10 (March 01, 2022)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Front-end dashboard store error<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.4.9 (Feb 16, 2022)<br \\/>\\nAdded: Store Category<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.4.8.2 (Dec 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFix : Auto redirect Membership checkout page<br \\/>\\nFix: Store contact form issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.8.1 (Dec 13, 2021)<br \\/>\\n Fixed: reCaptha issue for store contact form<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.8 (Dec 09, 2021)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Google Re-captcha V3 Support<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.7 (Nov 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Installing function not found issue<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.6.3 (Sep 28, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Review template loading issue<br \\/>\\nFixed: some coding issues<br \\/>\\nAdded: Addon filter to remove addon if installed<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.6.1 (Aug 13, 2021)<br \\/>\\nUpdate: Rest API<br \\/>\\nAdd: Control for Store contact info hide guest user. <\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.5 (July 28, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFixed: Mobile app Rest Api call issue<br \\/>\\nImpromove: Classified listing free version dependency Update<\\/p>\\n<p>Version 1.4.4 (Jun 24, 2021)<br \\/>\\nFix: Radius Search<br \\/>\\nImprove: code to work Classified Pro version 2.0<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.4.2 (April 15, 2021)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Store api connect for app<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.4.0 (Mar 14, 2021)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Store Manager feature<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.3.28(Aug 11, 2020)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Promotion under Membership package<br \\/>\\nversion 1.3.22 (April 30, 2020)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Archive page<br \\/>\\nAdd: Store Category<\\/p>\\n<p>version 1.3.10 (Dec 11, 2019)<br \\/>\\nAdd: Social Icon<br \\/>\\nAdd: Store Rating<br \\/>\\nAdd: 24h Store hrs format<\\/p>\\n<p>version 1.1.80 (May 23, 2019)<br \\/>\\nAdd nofollow link in store url<br \\/>\\nVersion 1.1.6 (Apr 25, 2019)<br \\/>\\nAdd settings store only for membership<\\/p>\\n\"]}\";}','off'),
