(1946,'_site_transient_update_plugins','O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:12:\"last_checked\";i:1782704874;s:8:\"response\";a:2:{s:53:\"classified-listing-store/classified-listing-store.php\";O:8:\"stdClass\":17:{s:4:\"name\";s:24:\"Store & Membership Addon\";s:11:\"new_version\";s:5:\"3.1.0\";s:14:\"stable_version\";s:5:\"3.1.0\";s:8:\"sections\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:11:\"description\";s:11548:\"<p>Classified Listing Store &amp; Membership addon				</p>\n<p>Create your store within in the Classified ads website so visitor can get all items easily under the store.</p>\n<p>					<a href=\"#pricing\"><br />\n									Pricing Plan<br />\n					</a><br />\n					<a href=\"https://www.radiustheme.com/docs/classified-listing/docs/listing-management-admin/stores-store-addon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n									Documentation<br />\n					</a></p>\n<p>Classified Listing is a fully responsive WordPress plugin by using this plugin you can create a classified listing website easily.</p>\n<p>Classified Listing plugin will work with any standard coding WordPress Theme.</p>\n<p>Classified plugins included all necessary features that need to build a classified listing website. It has wide range of back end settings for site admin and front end ad posting management system like user can add/ edit / delete his post any time.</p>\n<p>                                        Version:3.0.6					</p>\n<p>                                        Last updated:April 20, 2026					</p>\n<p>                                        Tested up to:6.9+<br />\n					Store &amp; Membership Features				</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n										Fully Responsive &amp; Mobile Friendly\n									</li>\n<li>\n										Membership &amp; Store facility\n									</li>\n<li>\n										Open Own store with store details &amp; Opening hours\n									</li>\n<li>\n										Allow Subscription Payment (Authorize.net and Stripe)\n									</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n										Get all ads under store.\n									</li>\n<li>\n										Can set Membership by Category wise or full site access.\n									</li>\n<li>\n										Can set no of free ad for a time interval.\n									</li>\n</ul>\n<p>					Membership Creation​				</p>\n<p>You can create membership package so user can chose which package they want, you can create membership by specific category wise or give access for all categories also can give free ads facility by category wise.</p>\n<p>					Membership Package​				</p>\n<p>You can create a membership package so users can choose which package they want, you can create membership by a specific category wise or give access for all categories also can give free ads facility by category wise.</p>\n<p>					Allow Subscription Payment				</p>\n<p>Membership payment will renew when you enable subscription. Right now Stripe and Authorize payment support subscription payment.</p>\n<p>					Create Your Own store				</p>\n<p>This is first time in WordPress classified plugin have store facility. We have store addon after enable this addon you will get membership option with store facility. User can add there store detail like own store banner with description, opening hrs etc..</p>\n<p>When any user visit the store page they get the all listings of the store.</p>\n<p>					Get Classified Store &amp; Membership  Addom				</p>\n<ul role=\"tablist\">\n<li><a>Yearly</a></li>\n<li>Big Save<a>All Adodns Bundle</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>									Popular<br />\n										1 Site License<br />\n                                                                                                                                            $29 / Yearly<br />\n			                            Renews at $23<br />\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.radiustheme.com/checkout?edd_action=add_to_cart&download_id=86410&edd_options[price_id]=1\"><br />\n                                            Purchase Now                                        </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Only Store &amp; Membership Addon</li>\n<li>1 Site or Domain</li>\n<li>1 Year Support</li>\n<li>1 Year Updates</li>\n<li>30 Days Money Back Guarantee</li>\n<li>20% Discount on Renewal</li>\n</ul>\n<p>									 Need Classified Listing Pro plugin<br />\n										5 Sites License<br />\n                                                                                                                                            $59 / Yearly<br />\n			                            Renews at $47<br />\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.radiustheme.com/checkout?edd_action=add_to_cart&download_id=86410&edd_options[price_id]=2\"><br />\n                                            Purchase Now                                        </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Only Store &amp; Membership Addon</li>\n<li>5 Sites or Domains</li>\n<li>1 Year Support</li>\n<li>1 Year Updates</li>\n<li>30 Days Money Back Guarantee</li>\n<li>20% Discount on Renewal</li>\n</ul>\n<p>									 Need Classified Listing Pro plugin<br />\n										Unlimited Sites License<br />\n                                                                                                                                            $99 / Yearly<br />\n			                            Renews at $79<br />\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.radiustheme.com/checkout?edd_action=add_to_cart&download_id=86410&edd_options[price_id]=3\"><br />\n                                            Purchase Now                                        </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Only Store &amp; Membership Addon</li>\n<li>Unlimited Sites or Domains</li>\n<li>1 Year Support</li>\n<li>1 Year Updates</li>\n<li>30 Days Money Back Guarantee</li>\n<li>20% Discount on Renewal</li>\n</ul>\n<p>									 Need Classified Listing Pro plugin<br />\n					.elementor-282397 .elementor-element.elementor-element-402afe2b{--display:flex;--gap:0px 0px;--row-gap:0px;--column-gap:0px;--padding-top:0px;--padding-bottom:0px;--padding-left:0px;--padding-right:0px;}.elementor-