age layout, delete option issue<br />\nUpdate: Settings integration with new layout<br />\nAdded: quick view and compare icon filter<br />\nUpdate: Compare content display issue for from builder custom field</p>\n<p>Version 4.0.3 (Aug 15, 2025)<br />\nAdded: Smart dependency logic at checkbox, radio, select field<br />\nFixed: Compare content display issue<br />\nFixed: get_avatar expect email or id but passed full comment object</p>\n<p>Version 4.0.2 (July 24, 2025)<br />\nFixed: Shortcode map view pagination issue<br />\nFixed: Form builder category, location field issue<br />\nFixed: Gallery show / hide issue<br />\nFixed: Video show / hide issue<br />\nFixed: Category widget column issue<br />\nAdded: Two action hooks for active map data ( rtcl_ajax_filter_query_before_loop, rtcl_ajax_filter_query_after_loop)</p>\n<p>Version 4.0.1 (July 16, 2025)<br />\nAdded: Image support at app push notification<br />\nAdded: Ajax filter: custom field filterable field apply conditional logic</p>\n<p>Version 4.0.0 (July 01, 2025)<br />\nUpdated: Reorganized admin settings<br />\nFixed: Popular badge show/hide issue</p>\n<p>Version 3.2.1 (June 13, 2025)<br />\nFixed: From builder – Conditional logic for check box field add includes and Not Includes operator<br />\nUpdated: Add login messages to start new chat<br />\nFixed: Mark as sold listing hidden issue when active filter/search<br />\nFixed: Chat message unread count issue<br />\nFixed: Chat body overflow scroll issue at chat for mobile</p>\n<p>Version 3.2.0 (May 27, 2025)<br />\nUpdated: Directory ajax filter field<br />\nAdded: Toolkit addon compatibility</p>\n<p>Version 3.1.2 (May 13, 2025)<br />\nFixed: Chat rtcl_conversation_messages table creating issue at new installation<br />\nVersion 3.1.1 (May 09, 2025)<br />\nFixed: Chat rest api: check conversation has started<br />\nFixed: My account chat list loading issue</p>\n<p>Version 3.1.0 (May 07, 2025)<br />\nUpdated: Page layout<br />\nAdded: Chat media/attachment upload<br />\nAdded: Chat admin back end for observe conversation<br />\nFixed: Elementor editor load issue<br />\nUpdated: Listing Slider Elementor addon<br />\nUpdated: Chat performance</p>\n<p>Version 3.0.5 (April 07, 2025)<br />\nAdded: Pusher configuration at config REST API<br />\nFixed: Sortable Search form issue</p>\n<p>Version 3.0.4 (Feb 21, 2025)<br />\nAdded: AI Power Form Generator and Write with AI.<br />\nFixed : Ajax filter Custom field: same field OR , different field AND relation<br />\nFixed: Custom field load issue at ajax filter<br />\nFixed: Duplicate top items at listings issue<br />\nUpdated: Chat performance updated<br />\nAdded: Pusher Added for update chat performance<br />\nAdded: remove beacon script<br />\nAdded: Pusher js for live chat<br />\nAdded: rtcl_user_online_status_seconds from js</p>\n<p>Version 3.0.3 (Feb 17, 2025)<br />\nAdded: Filter Hook Added (rtcl_is_chat_link_available)<br />\nFixed: Ajax Filter Date and Date Range filter issue</p>\n<p>Version 3.0.2 (Jan 31, 2025)<br />\nFixed: License key issue<br />\nFixed: Update REST API for APP</p>\n<p>Version 3.0.1 (Jan 13, 2025)<br />\nUpdated: Rest API (Add Form builder support for App)<br />\nFixed: Rest API kei generation issue<br />\nFixed: Listing excerpt limit for Elementor editor<br />\nFixed: Filter category rest API issue<br />\nFixed: Ajax filter number issue<br />\nAdded: Tag support at REST API</p>\n<p>Version 3.0.0 (Dec 20, 2024)<br />\nUpdated: REST API<br />\nUpdated: Menu Arrangement<br />\nAdded: Fontawesome 6 compatibility<br />\nAdded: Chat count<br />\nFixed: Text domain issue<br />\nFixed: Elementor Widgets Sortable Field Placeholder Text<br />\nFixed: Settings script load</p>\n<p>Version 2.4.3 (Nov 11, 2024)<br />\nAdded: Chat Count<br />\nVersion 2.4.2 (Nov 05, 2024)<br />\nFixed: Filter searching issue form select, radio, checkbox<br />\nAdded: Ajax Filter custom field sorting option</p>\n<p>Version 2.4.1 (Oct 01, 2024)<br />\nFixed: Is online fixed ajax error